data.description: PRICED BELOW APPRAISED VALUE, you can make this home your own!  Cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bath with extra space in the basement for whatever you need room for!  The hardwood floor in the living room has enough space to use part of it for a dining area.  Off of the kitchen is a fully screened patio, with tile floors.  Access from the alley to the 2 car garage.  Located within walking distance of the city park and the downtown area.  Make your appointment today!
